flowchart TB
    Root["Root CA<br/>Self-Signed Certificate<br/>Trust Anchor"]
    Intermediate["Intermediate CA<br/>Signed by Root CA"]
    Server["Server Certificate<br/>Signed by Intermediate CA"]
    Client["Client / Browser / Validator<br/>Trust Store contains Root CA"]

    Root -->|signs| Intermediate
    Intermediate -->|signs| Server
    Client -->|trusts| Root
    Client -->|validates chain| Server
